<plot>Donald Miller is freshly laid off and freshly single. He collapses into an introverted, single-minded quest to find a banana without any blemishes or bruises. His overbearing, struggling, graphic artist roommate, Marcy Dorris, relies on Donald for camaraderie as well as rent. Will Donald find his courage and put himself back on track?</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?582051</url></doc>
